title.rendered: Dolphy Airblade Jet Hand Dryer 1000 watt – WHITE

content.rendered:
Dolphy presents widest range of Hand Dryers suitable for Low to High traffic areas. These specially designed Hand Dryers are great addition to your Business washroom to create a Hygienic Environment.

Hand dryers are most effective way of drying hands and avoids the use of Paper towels making them environment friendly.

Specification:
Product Name: Airblade Jet Hand Dryer – Black
Product Code: DAHD0055
Colour: Black
Material: High Grade ABS
Motor Type: Brushed Motor
Voltage: AC220-240V / AC110-127V, 50/60Hz
Power: 1000 W
Air Speed: 90 m/s
Air Temperature: 20 ± 15°C
Noise level: 60-80 db(A)
Motor Speed: 25000 r/min
Drying time: <15 s
Water Splash Proof: IPX1
Dimension: 39.4 cm H x 23.1 cm W x 13.5 cm D
Warranty: 5 years warranty
Features:
High quality infrared sensor for automatic activation
Attractive design brings modern look to your washroom.
Touchless to prevent the spread of bacteria and the cross infection of the disease.
Running costs are up to 70% less than other hand dryers and  up to 98% less than paper towels.
As Automatic hand dryer with 100% clean air.
The absence of paper maintains a clean and hygienic environment.
Dolphy hand dryers use 85m/s speed of air to scrape water from hands like a windscreen wiper, drying them quickly and hygienically in less than 15 seconds.

excerpt.rendered:
Low & fair prices for high-quality goods
High customer satisfaction
Fast shipping, dispatched in two business days or less. Most metro orders are delivered within 1-4 working days.
100% secure shopping and safe checkout.
Australian trusted store, Australian based and owned. Your order is shipped from an Australian warehouse.
